Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, gcc, g++
Description: distributed C/C++ compiler with content-addressed caching
 SUCO is a distributed C/C++ compiler for LANs. It dispatches compile jobs
 across a worker grid with content-addressed caching, so warm rebuilds are
 served from cache and cold builds fan out over every node.
 .
 Ships the suco-cl/suco-cl++ compiler wrappers, the coordinator and worker
 daemons, and a web dashboard. Services are installed disabled; the admin
 enables each node's role with systemctl.
